Package org.aludratest.service

Interface Summary
Action Parent interface for all service actions which can provide file-based information useful for debugging.
AludraCloseable Parent interface for Aludratest classes that have a close() method.
AludraContext Common interface for AludraTest Contexts.
AludraService Common interface for all services that can be tested by AludraTest.
AludraServiceContext Interface for AludraService contexts.
AludraServiceManager The bootstrap for Aludra Components like e.g. services.
Condition Common interface for accessing state information of a system under test.
Interaction Common interface for interacting with a system under test.
ServiceWrapper  
SystemConnector Callback interface for systems to provide information about asynchronous state changes of the system under test, e.g. busy indication or system error reports.
SystemConnectorInterface Parent interface for interfaces available for SystemConnector.getConnector(Class).
Verification Common interface for verifying the state of a system under test.
 

Class Summary
AbstractAludraService Abstract parent class for custom AludraService implementations.
AbstractConfigurableAludraService Abstract parent class for AludraTest service implementations which are configurable.
ComponentId<T> Identifier for an AludraTest component, e.g. a service.
 

Annotation Types Summary
Implementation Marks an implementation of a service or component interface.
ServiceInterface This annotation marks an Interface as Aludra Service interface, i.e. it can be used in a call to AludraTestCase.getService(ComponentId) as interface class in the component ID.
